{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-05-24-2",
 "title": "An Odd Civilian in the Hangar",
 "summary": "Returning to the Pride 1 hangar bay to rest after his Death Star talks, the disguised NRI agent Bazil McKenzie (as Mege Vauki) crosses paths again with the Griffon cargo hauler Khirsah, whom he had earlier glimpsed on a holoterm. Nearby, the Griffon officer Dekker dismisses a subordinate named Lokiar after praising his leadership. Bazil and Khirsah strike up an easy conversation about cargo runs, profitable routes, and the grind of hauling, sizing each other up while Khirsah quietly notes the expensive blaster on the weary civilian's hip. Recognizing how exhausted Bazil looks, Khirsah cuts the small talk short, the two shake hands and part with a shared hunch they will meet again, and Bazil boards the Triton and departs.",
